WHAT
------
I did some snippets in order to make my life easier and I believe that it can help you too. I extended the Javascript snippets, put another Javascripts functions and I also put a lot of jQuery functions.


Documentation
------
If you want an overview of all jQuery and javascript snippets available, take a look into the documentation http://www.danielcamargo.com.br/stuffs/gedit-snippets-jquery/documentation.php. 

Install 
------
$ git clone git://github.com/pererinha/gedit-snippet-jquery.git
$ cp gedit-snippets/snippets/*.xml ~/.gnome2/gedit/snippets 

More information about Gedit Snippets
------
http://live.gnome.org/Gedit/Plugins/Snippets

